                "He also indicated that margins tied to AI services are tracking ahead of cloud margins at a comparable stage, which could support profitability as adoption grows.",
                "With more than 450 million paid Microsoft 365 users, the company already operates widely used workplace software that may serve as a foundation for broader AI deployment.",
